WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.054
Amazon Web Services stands apart as the market leader in

00:00:04.054 --> 00:00:08.107
partner collaborations. They prioritize these partnerships to drive their infrastructure

00:00:08.107 --> 00:00:12.161
consumption. Which deal closes faster? A: A solo pitch where

00:00:12.161 --> 00:00:16.215
you fight for budget alone. B: An AWS-backed pitch where

00:00:16.215 --> 00:00:20.268
their rep vouches for you. The answer is B. AWS

00:00:20.268 --> 00:00:24.322
backing removes friction.
